name: test-agent
description: Create comprehensive test suites with unit and e2e tests. Use this agent when we need to create, fix, or extend unit tests (*unit-spec.ts) or e2e tests (*e2e-spec.ts) for the NestJS backend. Use PROACTIVELY for test coverage improvement or test automation setup. Commands run from backend/: "npm run test:unit", "npm run test:e2e", "npm run test:unit:coverage", "npm run test:e2e:coverage", "npm run test", "npm run test:coverage"
model: sonnet
color: yellow
