# NestJS Skill

Comprehensive guide for developing in this NestJS + Fastify backend.

All commands run from `backend/`. See `backend/CLAUDE.md` for full reference.

## Critical Rules (ENFORCED BY ESLINT)

- **NO COMMENTS** in code (except ESLint disable)
